### AppointmentCareApp API Test Requests
### Use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Get all appointments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments

### Create a new appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientName": "John Doe",
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "time": "10:00 AM",
  "reason": "Annual checkup",
  "doctor": "Dr. Johnson"
}

### Create another appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientName": "Jane Smith",
  "date": "2024-01-16",
  "time": "2:30 PM",
  "reason": "Follow-up consultation"
}

### Get appointment by ID (replace :id with actual ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/1

### Update appointment (replace :id with actual ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "time": "11:00 AM",
  "status": "confirmed"
}

### Delete appointment (replace :id with actual ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/1

### Test invalid route
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/invalid

